      • computeFDList

        public abstract java.util.ArrayList<java.util.Map.Entry<E,java.lang.Integer>> computeFDList(java.util.ArrayList<E> dataSet)
        Determines the frequency distribution of objects in a particular dataset using a valid strategy. It is based on the algorithm defining the particular strategy to solve the frequency counting problem.
        Parameters:
        dataSet - the dataset of objects to be analized
        Returns:
        a list of entries, where each such entry is a pair: key (of type E) is a reference to one instance of a different object , and value is the frequency of that object in the list being analyzed
